casebody.data:
No. 11-6774. Pamela Cadenhead, Petitioner v. Michael J. Astrue, Commissioner of Social Security. 565 U.S. 1078, 132 S. Ct. 836,

181 L. Ed. 2d 524,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8776. December 5, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner is allowed until December 27, 2011, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 410 Fed. Appx. 982.
